From c613635c2fc051557a29861139e41ca8b320e089 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: local <local@hermes>
Date: Mon, 20 Apr 2026 15:31:45 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Custom provider enhancements: custom:<name> resolution + live
 /models probing

These changes add two features to support multiple named custom providers
(like Chutes) from config.yaml:

1. provider_model_ids(custom:<name>) - resolves the named custom provider
   from config, probes its /models endpoint, and returns live model list.

2. list_authenticated_providers() section 4 - extracts api_key from
   custom_providers entries and probes live /models endpoint to discover
   models beyond what is declared in config.

Both changes are purely additive and preserve all upstream dedup,
User-Agent, and validation logic.
